54
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:28,340
watching people press their ugly faces in on you.

55
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,780
Can you hear me?

56
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:40,340
It's just, I've never talked to a snake before.

57
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:42,220
Do you?

58
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:46,540
Do you talk to people often?

59
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:50,980
You're from Burma, aren't you? Was it nice there?

60
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:53,460
