00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:06,990
Mummy, what's happening?

101
00:13:10,430 --> 00:13:14,750
Give me that! Give me that letter!

102
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:19,150
Get off!

103
00:13:22,910 --> 00:13:27,070
They're my letters! Let go of me!

104
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:30,910
That's it! We're going away!

105
00:13:31,590 --> 00:13:35,230
Far away, where they can't find us!

106
00:13:35,470 --> 00:13:38,710
Daddy's gone mad, hasn't he?

107
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:15,910
Make a wish, Harry.

108
00:14:31,990 --> 00:14:34,070
Who's there?

109
00:14:46,230 --> 00:14:48,670
Sorry about that.

110
00:14:55,550 --> 00:15:00,110
I demand that you leave at once. You are breaking and entering.

111
00:15:02,990 --> 00:15:05,830
Dry up, Dursley, you great prune.

112
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:14,550
I haven't seen you since you was a baby, Harry.

113
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:17,470
You're a bit more along than I expected.

114
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,310
Particularly in the middle.

115
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:22,350
I'm not Harry.

116
00:15:24,190 --> 00:15:27,910
- I am. - Well, of course you are.

117
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,270
Got something for you.

118
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:36,070
Afraid I sat on it, but I imagine it'll taste fine just the same.

119
00:15:38,590 --> 00:15:41,990
Baked it myself, words and all.

120
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,590
Thank you.

121
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:52,950
It's not every day your young man turns 11, is it?

122
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:12,270
Excuse me, but who are you?

123
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:17,390
Rubeus Hagrid, Keeper of Keys and Grounds at Hogwarts.

124
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:21,350
- Of course, you know about Hogwarts. - Sorry, no.

125
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:26,870
Didn't you ever wonder where your mum and dad learned it all?

126
00:16:27,110 --> 00:16:28,510
Learned what?

127
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:31,270
You're a wizard, Harry.

128
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,510
- I'm a what? - A wizard.

129
00:16:34,710 --> 00:16:37,750
A good one, I'd wager, once you're trained up.

130
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:40,870
No, you've made a mistake. I mean

131
00:16:41,110 --> 00:16:44,110
I can't be a wizard.

132
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:49,510
I mean, I'm just Harry. Just Harry.

133
00:16:50,590 --> 00:16:54,590
Well, Just Harry, did you ever make anything happen?

134
00:16:54,830 --> 00:16:59,470
Anything you couldn't explain, when you were angry or scared?

135
00:17:15,870 --> 00:17:18,990
"Dear Mr. Potter, We are pleased to accept you

136
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:22,470
at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. "

137
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:24,250
He will not be going I tell you!

138
00:17:24,250 --> 00:17:27,630
