00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:48,100
And there's something else as well.

217
00:24:49,340 --> 00:24:52,660
Professor Dumbledore gave me this.

218
00:24:56,740 --> 00:25:01,820
It's about You-Know-What in vault you-know-which.

